#title "SegaPCM Genesis Example"
#description "SegaPCM synthesis on Sega Genesis - PCM drum and bass samples"

$Genesis1=SegaPCM@1
$Genesis2=SegaPCM@2

* Drums Channel
@Genesis1
@BANK0
t120 l16
o4 c8 r8 d8 r8 | e8 r8 f8 r8 | g8 r8 a8 r8 | b8 r8 >c8 r8

* Bass Channel
@Genesis2
@BANK0
t120 l8
o2 c4 c4 | g4 g4 | a4 a4 | f4 f4
